title: Dallas 10x27 The Dark at the End of the Tunnel.avi
description:
Yes boys and girls: DALLAS is back, and now that the dream is over, its even better than ever!

J.R. acquires Bobby, Ray, and Miss Ellie's shares of Ewing Oil, and is tested for loyalty by Sue Ellen; April seeks revenge for past wrongs against her; Clayton confronts J.R.

First Aired: 5/01/1987

In this episode Bobby says he has Gary Ewing's power of attorney and Gary will agree to sell his holdings in Ewing Oil to J.R., but this storyline didn't and couldn't have been mentioned on Knot's Landing because Bobby Ewing was dead on Knot's Landing by this time and the two shows stopped interacting.
